These are in the 2xx range, meaning the request worked:

- 200 OK – Everything worked as expected.
- 201 Created – Something was successfully created (common for APIs).
- 202 Accepted – Request accepted but not processed yet.
- 204 No Content – Request succeeded but there’s nothing to show (e.g., after deletion).
